{"release_time": "2024-10-06 18:31:13", "update_time": "2024-10-06 18:31:17", "description": {"title": "豆瓣影视榜单列表", "subtitle": "最近热门国产剧", "source": "https://m.douban.com/subject_collection/tv_domestic", "link": "https://m.douban.com/rexxar/api/v2/subject_collection/tv_domestic/items", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "page_total": 1, "page_limit": -1, "item_total": null, "item_limit": 20, "page_count": 1, "sup_page_count": 0, "my-query-id": "tv_domestic"}, "extra": {}, "stats": {"movies": 20}, "movies": [{"comment": "该剧根据“七一勋章”获得者张桂梅事迹改编。\n张桂梅（宋佳 饰）是中国西部山区的一名普通中学女教师，多年间她不断目睹自己的女学生因家庭贫穷而辍学，在15、16岁的年纪或嫁人生子、或外出打工，这让张桂梅无比痛心和惋惜。她立志要办一所全免费的女子高中，让这些大山里的女孩获得受教育的机会、能够考上大学、走出大山，彻底改变 命运。2008年，全中国唯一一所全免费的女子高中成立，在没老师、没学生、没经费、没经验的重重困境下，张桂梅带领女高师生们完成了不可能的任务：让学习基础极度落后的女高学生们，全部考上了大学。这所女子高中让一批批女孩走出了大山，改变了命运。然而随着学校的发展，越来越多大山里贫困女生前来报考，新的问题和困难也随之而来……", "rating": {"count": 86569, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 9.3}, "vendor_count": 1, "has_linewatch": true, "title": "山花烂漫时", "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2912813745.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2912813745.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [{"kind": "tv", "uri": "douban://douban.com/subject_collection/EC74443FY?type=rank&category=movie&rank_type=tv_genre", "rank": 2, "title": "近期热门大陆剧榜"}], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/35496807", "episodes_info": "23集全", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2902565008.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2902565074.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2902565073.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2913352068.jpg"], "vendor_icons": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/f/frodo/fbc90f355fc45d5d2056e0d88c697f9414b56b44/pics/vendors/tencent.png"], "interest": null, "year": "2024", "card_subtitle": "2024 / 中国大陆 / 剧情 / 费振翔 / 宋佳 兰西雅", "recommend_comment": "内娱这个烂摊子只有女编剧女编导女编导能救 —— momo的短评", "type": "tv", "id": "35496807", "tags": []}, {"comment": "讲述了1950年前后，在上海